locality: Flora of the Republic of South Africa. Western Cape Province. Worcester District. Junction of Villiersdorp-Grabouw road with road to Franschhoek just N of Theewaterskloofdam. NW corner of intersection.
Flora of the Republic of South Africa. Western Cape Province. Ladismith District. Grootberg. Around upper summit slopes (N side).
Algeria, behind house of assistent forester. N slope rock cover 70%. Vegetation cover 30% (70% of which are Restionaceae and Cyperaceae), height 40-50 cm burnt April 1984.
Kanonkop, Atlantis steep W slope. Granite hill with deep loamy substrate, rock cover 10% vegetation cover 60% (15% of which Restionaceae); height 30-40 cm; occasional Eucalyptus.
